
################## deprecated benchmarks

# calculations as in DY pheno paper 2024
# divides theory by a normalization to model systematic uncertainties
# (dividing is consistent with D'Agostini paper, which we cited in our work)



  E288_control_ninv: computes chi2 with fixed parameter which values were obtained in paper
                     calculation is done using the same data points of E288 as in the paper

  E288_control_ninv_fast: computes chi2 with fixed parameter which values were obtained in paper
                          calculation is done using only a few points, for fast calculation





################## current benchmarks

# multiplies theory by a normalization to model systematic uncertainties
# from now on code uses rhis version, it is simpler to implement and equivalent
# to the one used in the paper

  E288_control: fit to the same E288 data points as in our paper.
                writes Minuit covariance matrix and calculated other related quantities,
                placed inside 'cov/' subfolder


  E288_control_fast: computes chi2 with fixed parameters, which values were obtained in
                     benchmark fit 'E288_control'. Calculation is done on all points.
